Demi Bold: Headlines, sub-headers, pull-quotes, captions
Regular: All body copy
Italic variants: Available for both weights
Fallback Font Families

‚úÖ International: "Noto Sans" (when Avenir Next World doesn't support the language)
Bold and Bold Italic available
‚úÖ Video/External: "Montserrat" (for video intros and external packages)
Bold, SemiBold, Medium, Regular (all with italic variants)
‚úÖ PowerPoint: "Avenir Next LT Pro" (free on Microsoft font library)
Typography Usage Guidelines

‚úÖ Text Color: Primary 
#252526 on white backgrounds, white on black backgrounds
‚úÖ Alignment: Left or center aligned (avoid right alignment)
‚úÖ Tracking: Keep at default (0) - don't adjust tracking
‚úÖ Leading: Use default settings, avoid too tight or too loose spacing
‚úÖ Gradient Text: Selective use of brand gradient colors in headlines only (adjacent words only, single gradient across words)
